<recipe>
<title>
Coconut Almond Overnight Oats
</title>
<details>
PREP TIME: 5 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 5 minutes
SERVINGS: 2
</details>
<ingredients>
1 c . QuakerÂ® Old Fashioned Rolled Oats
1 c . 1% low-fat milk
1/3 c . coconut yogurt
Sweetened shredded coconut
Sliced Almonds
Unsweetened cocoa powder
</ingredients>
<instructions>
In a small bowl, stir together oats, milk, and yogurt.
Cover, and refrigerate overnight.
In the morning, top with coconut, almonds, and a dusting of cocoa powder, if desired.
</instructions>
</recipe>
